⁣It took me a while but I think I've officially caught onto the homemade pizza craze- ⠀
Octopus, burrata, asparagus, and a JB ah meng-inspired white pepper clam sauce on a 70% hydration, 24-hour fermented dough⠀
⠀
The shape is oval cause I had so much trouble transferring the dough onto my baking surface, still a long long way more to go but I'd say this was a pretty good first try. Super excited to try and perfect the dough and all the possible toppings that could come along with it 😍
🤤🤤🤤...the crust is just nice and not so thick... 👏👏👏
@lennardy japan’s tomato game is strong 🍅🍅🍅 I’ve been eating all kinds of new varieties
The bubbles trapped in the dough though! Just wow! Kudos 👌
@iammirkofebbrile ahahah so next time I shouldn't make it round
Looking good and tasty! Very good fermentation and also, Napoli pizza is never perfect round 😎👏🏻
@heyrozz sounds like another live vid cookout session!
@heyrozz dough it to me too pls🖤
i need the recipe for the JB ah meng white pepz sosss
@designer_chap 🤤 still prefer my orh ngeng tho
Where can I find the recipe for the pizza base? Thx!
where are the octopus legs of the pizza? D:<
My last pizza was bacterium 🦠 shape 😂😂😂it’s no easy to make a perfect circle ⭕️
